Traffic Light
ECEN 2350
Ben Cavins
(benjamin.cavins@colorado.edu)

============================================================
    FILES
============================================================

  - TrafficLight.v
  - Clock100and1.c
  - SevenSegmentDisplay.v
  - README

============================================================
    SETTING UP ON DE0
============================================================

    element: DE0 PIN

  - ClkIn: 5MHz clock
  - Resetn: Button2
  - Sensor: Switch0
  - ssd[0-3]: HEX[0-3] (seven-segment displays)

============================================================
    CONTROLS
============================================================

  HEX3 and HEX2 display the one-second counter, HEX1 
  displays the current state, HEX0 displays the traffic 
  light configuration. 

  Switch0 controlls the farm road vehicle sensor, Button0 
  resets the machine. 